Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.28,0:01:21.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,when i was a kid,\Nin a crazy dream
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.39,0:01:23.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,i was gazin' up to\Nthe promised land
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.16,0:01:27.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僕らのユメの形　ザワメキ出す heart！ beat！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.79,0:01:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,come on let's go to that place
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.14,0:01:31.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,i just can't stop anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.01,0:01:36.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛びだせ　仄暗い空　fly into the light
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.85,0:01:40.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信じたいこの世界に生まれたことが幸せってこと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.43,0:01:43.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新時代へ続く扉を開けるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.03,0:01:45.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,wow wow oh oh oh.
